I"Ð<h2 id="about-the-course">About the course</h2>

<p><img src="./images/critialmaking3dweek_pixelated.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>This semester course taught at the Amsterdam University of Applied Sciences challenges you to think critically about the way you make and design. You acquire hands-on knowledge and skills that enable you to experience how things might be made differently and discover alternatives to reduce the environmental impact of man-made things.</p>
